threads.title: 820-00281-A 20v BUT 0 mAh
threads.message:

[B]PP5V_S5 = 2V to 5V in Loop!
[B]PP5V_S3 = 2V to 5V in Loop![/B][/B]

Any hint from here?

threads.message:
Do you get pulse on all secondary voltages, or S3 at least?
Also check ALL_SYS_PWRGD.
